          "percent": [
            14.179775280898877,
            -5.0703125
          ],
          "description": "Boramas is the capital city of house Aegir. It is a shining territory with wealth displayed around every corner. The city originally had problems with poor people being cast into the shadows and brought to starvation, but now the young lord has taken care that all peoples are given a chance to thrive in the domain.",
